Unlike conspiracy theorists, I think counting is much less likely to be manipulated. But there is really nothing that prevents ballot harvesting of paper ballots. Some people do not care to vote. But they'd happily give up their paper ballot for $.

https://t.co/SUtp8c2fXQ

The Republicans who say we should just accept whatever the cheating gets us are not thinking of this country - Americans better think twice - there are going to be concentration camps in this country. Ballot harvesting of phony ballots should not be allowed.
